10  package de.funfried.netbeans.plugins.external.formatter.java.google;
11  
12  /**
13   * Utility class for Google Java formatter specific settings.
14   *
15   * @author bahlef
16   */
17  public class GoogleJavaFormatterSettings {
18  	/**
19  	 * Property key which defines which code style should be used for the Google formatter.
20  	 *
21  	 * @since 1.13
22  	 */
23  	public static final String CODE_STYLE = "googleFormatterCodeStyle";
24  
25  	/**
26  	 * Property key which defines if the Google formatter internal organize imports action should be used.
27  	 *
28  	 * @since 1.15.2
29  	 */
30  	public static final String ORGANIZE_IMPORTS = "googleFormatterOrganizeImports";
31  
32  	/**
33  	 * Property key which defines if the Google formatter internal organize imports action should be used after NetBeans fix import action was executed.
34  	 *
35  	 * @since 1.15.2
36  	 */
37  	public static final String ORGANIZE_IMPORTS_AFTER_FIX_IMPORTS = "googleFormatterOrganizeImportsAfterFixImports";
38  
39  	/**
40  	 * Private contructor because of static methods only.
41  	 */
42  	private GoogleJavaFormatterSettings() {
43  	}
44  }
